{"tid":2231823,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"卡雲尼成日都證明自己勁過呂布 有冇巴打期待佢10月21日歐聯報復PSG","createTime":"2020-10-06T03:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T13:12:31.000Z","uid":84081,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"8f6a377228fdda855fbec02087cebe561d162d18","tid":2231823,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T03:00:50.000Z","msg":"PSG仲有伊巴個陣<br />\n次次後備上陣都入至少一球<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n伊巴喺英超證明咗自己 依家卡雲尼又黎挑戰 仲好似著埋7號 <br />\n卡雲尼有支點能力 起碼好過中超同馬兩個BLM先 破密集對中下游好大幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唯一問題係教練蘇查識唔識用佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n來回高速球對攻就唔太啱佢 始終年齡大咗 頭幾場仲有體能紅利 之後隨時好似伊巴咁傷<br />\n最好都係面對密集 佢有埋處理罰波能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對PSG佢仲有體能可能都復到仇 但係面對利物浦同曼城佢就冇咩優勢了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔緊要啦 都係木狗衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 卡雲尼係無辜既"},{"pid":"93fd3a3023f484a5189e12f767162e5f0fb748a9","tid":2231823,"uid":34571,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T03:16:14.000Z","msg":"著七號就知佢會敗走"},{"pid":"38fbceb1517984a8f037fc78f28a69d75be37371","tid":2231823,"uid":45498,"like":5,"dislike":15,"score":-10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T03:23:26.000Z","msg":"卡雲屁無勁過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢啲埋門一腳真係街場都不如"},{"pid":"5b17cbce8395c7a3b89f2efddbcf955d0876456f","tid":2231823,"uid":84081,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T03:32: